{"type":"message","id":"ae3b873f","parentId":"e65d8c02","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:12:01.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa2cb476ac0e4841b66937e8","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### 5.2 SDD 对效率的反噬与应对","oldText":"### 5.2 递归问题：谁来保证规格是对的？"}],"file_path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-sdd-special/sdd-article.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95090,"output":77,"cacheRead":11136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106303,"cost":{"input":0.114108,"output":0.000308,"cacheRead":0.0026726399999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11708864000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775639475902,"responseId":"20260408171135239a843cba874823"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d6bca77","parentId":"ae3b873f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:12:01.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa2cb476ac0e4841b66937e8","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-sdd-special/sdd-article.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 437 为什么这么说？可以打个比方：没有类型系统的编程语言，代码能跑，但你不知道对不对——编译器帮你在早期排除了一大类低级错误（语法错误、类型不匹配等），但不能保证程序逻辑正确。规格对 AI 生成的代码扮演着类似的角色——它不能保证 AI 写出完美的代码，但能排除\"AI 做了规格没说的事\"和\"AI 没做规格说的事\"这两类最基本的错误。\n 438 \n 439 没有规格的 AI 编码，就像没有编译器的编程——能跑，但你不知道它到底做了什么。\n 440 \n-441 ### 5.2 递归问题：谁来保证规格是对的？\n+441 ### 5.2 SDD 对效率的反噬与应对\n 442 \n 443 这里有一个看似无解的递归问题：\n 444 \n 445 1. AI 写代码 → 谁来保证代码做的是对的事？→ 用规格验证。\n     ...","firstChangedLine":441},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775639521457}}
{"type":"message","id":"a54356e4","parentId":"7d6bca77","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:12:38.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改好了。标题更准确了，内容讲的就是 SDD 引入的额外审查成本可能吞噬 AI 带来的效率优势，以及四个应对思路。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":160,"output":35,"cacheRead":106176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106371,"cost":{"input":0.000192,"output":0.00014,"cacheRead":0.025482239999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025814239999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775639521464,"responseId":"20260408171224f8738121b1a545c5"}}
