{"type":"message","id":"1307d9ba","parentId":"08f8d5c0","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:00:45.313Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c6316fa6089446ec81185bd2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Adrian Cockcroft vibe coding software crisis netflix\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 4042,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f2982e9e4465459d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Vibe Coding Threatens Open Source: Investigative Report\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f2982e9e4465459d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://netcrook.com/ai-vibe-coding-open-source-crisis/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6981848559f8dfa2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI-powered vibe coding is changing the way developers interact with open source, posing risks to community engagement, innovation, and software diversity.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6981848559f8dfa2\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"netcrook.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"354259eb75e9b26f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVibe Coding 2026: 2,000 Vulnerabilities, 400 Exposed Secrets, Zero ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"354259eb75e9b26f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://mvidmar.substack.com/p/vibe-coding-2000-vulnerabilities-ai-software-subprime-security-crisis-2026\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c726c697d850d1af\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVibe coding is software's subprime crisis . And this article is the audit. The Greatest Construction Boom in History To understand the scale of what's happening, look at the numbers. Not opinions, not forecasts: numbers. Cursor, the world's most popular AI-assisted coding tool, hit $2 billion in annual recurring revenue (ARR) in February 2026.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c726c697d850d1af\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"mvidmar.substack.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"94b5706f939b2f66\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhy Vibe Coding Is Going to Create the Worst Software Crisis ... - Medium\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"94b5706f939b2f66\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://medium.com/@Reiki32/why-vibe-coding-is-going-to-create-the-worst-software-crisis-in-history-1a0b666a9b0c\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6c759fbd6b0dacdd\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhy Vibe Coding Is Going to Create the Worst Software Crisis in History In February 2025, Andrej Karpathy, former AI lead at Tesla and OpenAI co-founder, coined a term that would define the year …\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6c759fbd6b0dacdd\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"medium.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"28dfcafdea46dd18\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMicroservices Retrospective - What We Learned (and Didn't ... - InfoQ\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"28dfcafdea46dd18\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/microservices-netflix-industry/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"912a3eda2c468a06\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdrian Cockcroft does a retrospective on microservices, what they set out to do at Netflix , how it worked out, and how things have subsequently permeated across the industry.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"912a3eda2c468a06\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.infoq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1efac2e847384192\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdrian Cockcroft - Nubank | LinkedIn\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT 