s most popular AI-assisted coding tool, hit $2 billion in annual recurring revenue (ARR) in February 2026.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c726c697d850d1af\">>>","siteName":"mvidmar.substack.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"94b5706f939b2f66\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhy Vibe Coding Is Going to Create the Worst Software Crisis ... - Medium\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"94b5706f939b2f66\">>>","url":"https://medium.com/@Reiki32/why-vibe-coding-is-going-to-create-the-worst-software-crisis-in-history-1a0b666a9b0c","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6c759fbd6b0dacdd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhy Vibe Coding Is Going to Create the Worst Software Crisis in History In February 2025, Andrej Karpathy, former AI lead at Tesla and OpenAI co-founder, coined a term that would define the year …\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6c759fbd6b0dacdd\">>>","siteName":"medium.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"28dfcafdea46dd18\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMicroservices Retrospective - What We Learned (and Didn't ... - InfoQ\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"28dfcafdea46dd18\">>>","url":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/microservices-netflix-industry/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"912a3eda2c468a06\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdrian Cockcroft does a retrospective on microservices, what they set out to do at Netflix , how it worked out, and how things have subsequently permeated across the industry.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"912a3eda2c468a06\">>>","siteName":"www.infoq.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1efac2e847384192\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdrian Cockcroft - Nubank | LinkedIn\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1efac2e847384192\">>>","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/adriancockcroft","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"44d869b14b5e358a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdrian Cockcroft Greater Salinas Area 22K followers